These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, police-officer, software-developer, doctor, lawyer, security-guard
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, colombian, dutch, pakistani, spanish, russian
 1. the software-developer is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the pakistani is the software-developer##1
 3. the security-guard is on the right of the lawyer##1
 4. the colombian is on the right of the spanish##1
 5. the police-officer is in the middle##1
 6. the japanese is on the far left##1
 7. the doctor is the japanese##1
 8. the firefighter is on the right of the spanish##1
 9. the colombian is on the left of the brazilian##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the police-officer##1
11. the security-guard is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | doctor | software-developer | freelancer | police-officer | firefighter | lawyer | security-guard |
| Nationality   | japanese    | pakistani   | dutch      | spanish | colombian    | brazilian    | russian         |

