.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, asparagus, pumpkin, pomegranate, lemon, corn, pear
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, electronic, jazz, metal, blues, hip-hop, country
 1. the fan of blues is the person eating pomegranate##1
 2. the person eating corn is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 7. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 9. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
10. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | grapefruit | asparagus | lemon | pomegranate | corn | pear | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | jazz   | metal   | blues      | reggae       | country       | hip-hop     |

