.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, orange, broccoli, apricot, watermelon, pineapple, pumpkin
The people have 7 different jobs:  doctor, lawyer, designer, software-developer, social-worker, coach, fisherman
 1. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the fisherman##1
 3. the lawyer is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 5. the doctor is the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the lawyer##1
 7. the lawyer is on the left of the designer##1
 8. the lawyer is on the right of the software-developer##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is the software-developer##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the doctor##1
11. the software-developer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | orange | watermelon     | broccoli  | pineapple       | garlic       | pumpkin  | apricot   |
| Job    | coach  | doctor | fisherman | software-developer | lawyer | designer | social-worker |

