.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, reggae, blues, punk, soul, trance, techno
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, polish, brazilian, turkish, chinese, dutch, malaysian
 1. the fan of soul is the polish##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the dutch is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
 7. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the fan of blues is the chinese##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
11. the malaysian is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | techno     | punk     | blues      | reggae | soul      | classical     |
| Nationality   | turkish | brazilian | dutch | chinese | malaysian | polish | russian |

