.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing, filmmaking, baking, hiking, reading, writing
7 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, turtle, hamster, hedgehog, lizard, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | dancing | filmmaking | reading     | baking | writing | hiking | skydiving |
| Pet     | rat   | turtle    | hedgehog | lizard     | mouse         | hamster     | ferret        |

