.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, mirinda, tea, cola
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, motorbike, van, boat, scooter, subway
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person drinking water is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | lemonade | tea   | water | milk | cola  | mirinda | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | van   | boat | helicopter | scooter     | roller | subway | motorbike   |

