.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, scientific, family, spy, thriller, epic
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, ship, tram, scooter, subway, car, quad-bike
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person driving the train is the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | epic | family | spy | thriller     | romance | scientific |
| Transport     | car | scooter      | quad-bike | tram    | subway | ship   | train  |

